### Step 2: Calculate Debt to Asset Ratio

- Total Assets = $33,082,821.36
- Debt to Asset Ratio = $3,143,833.89 / $33,082,821.36 = 0.095 = 0.10

### Step 3: Calculate Gross Profit Margin
Gross Profit Margin = Gross Profit / Total Revenue
- Gross Profit = $6,476,677.56
- Total Revenue = $22,876,677.56
- Gross Profit Margin = $6,476,677.56 / $22,876,677.56 = 0.2831 = 28.31%
